Chipotle Chicken Burrito

$12.5
750 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

MexicanWrapSpicy

Description

A zesty and hearty burrito packed with marinated chicken, black beans, and a blend of savory spices, wrapped in a warm tortilla for a fulfilling meal.

Ingredients

  • Chicken Breast: 1 lb
  • Black Beans: 1 cup
  • Brown Rice: 1 cup
  • Tortilla: 2 large
  • Cheddar Cheese: 1 cup
  • Sour Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Pico de Gallo: 1/2 cup
  • Avocado: 1
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup
  • Lime Juice: 2 tbsp
